      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "着替えてきたわよ\nほら、私をよく見てちょうだい",
      "startTime": 146.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "あ……",
      "startTime": 150.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "え？　どうしたの？",
      "startTime": 151.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "すみません……その衣装\n凄く似合ってて綺麗ですし、びっくりしちゃって",
      "startTime": 157.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
